Interface StateParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SerializableCartPoleStateFactory.CartPoleStateParser, SerializableFrostbiteStateFactory.FrostbiteStateParser, SerializableGridWorldStateFactory.GridWorldStateParser, SerializableInvertedPendulumStateFactory.InvertedPendulumStateParser, SerializableLunarLanderStateFactory.LunarLanderStateParser, SerializableMountainCarStateFactory.MountainCarStateParser, StateJSONParser, StateYAMLParser

    public interface StateParser
    This interface is used to converting states to parsable string representations and parsing those string representations back into states. Although there is a domain-universal string parser implementation of this interface, it is very verbose and file size and readability may be improved by creating a domain-specific state parser.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
